	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=157153><span id=Guru>aanil</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>26 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;All worn effects of the Aura series stack with each other.  If you have two Aura of Bravery and two Aura of Battle items, you will recive the full effect (otherwise melee/hybrid elemental armour sets would be rather senseless).  These effects also stack with all other worn atk and regen effects - Vengeance, Spiritual Fury, etc.  Furthmore, an item with the same effect both as part of the item and from an Augmentation will recieve both effects.<br>  However there is a cap of 250 worn ATK from all effects.  There is also a worn regeneration cap, which I believe is 35/tick.<br></p>&nbsp;<br>[65 Forest Stalker] Aanil &lt;Infinit&gt;<br></td></tr>
